          <p>Burlington currently has no specific short-term rental bylaws, making it an attractive market for both homeowners and investors. Check our <a href="/blog/burlington-airbnb-short-term-rental-rules-2026">Burlington STR rules guide</a> for the latest regulatory updates. This flexibility, combined with strong tourist demand, creates an ideal environment for Airbnb hosting.</p>
        </div>
